short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Right click on a Sencha page, Select 'Log this object'

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you use a Sencha framework, you can use this to right click on an item on your chrome browser, and log the object to the console for debugging purposes.

Only tested on EXT JS.
